# ServiceNow User Access Management with Workflow Automation

## Project Overview

This project demonstrates the implementation of a secure **User, Group, Role Management System** in **ServiceNow** using Role-Based Access Control (RBAC), Access Control Lists (ACLs), and Flow Designer automation.

The application provides controlled access for different users while automating task assignment, approvals, and notifications to improve operational efficiency and governance.

---

## Features

* User Management

  * Create users (Alice and Bob)
  * Assign user roles

* Group Management

  * Create Project Team Group
  * Add users to the group

* Role Management

  * Project Manager Role
  * Team Member Role

* Custom Tables

  * Project Table
  * Task Table

* Application Modules

  * Project Module
  * Task Module

* Access Control Lists (ACLs)

  * Full access for Project Manager
  * Restricted access for Team Member
  * Bob can update only **Status** and **Comments** fields

* Workflow Automation

  * Automatic task status updates
  * Approval workflow
  * Notification to Project Manager

