## User Roles

### Project Manager (Alice)

Responsibilities:

* Create Projects
* Assign Tasks
* Monitor Progress
* Approve Completed Tasks
* Full access to all project records

### Team Member (Bob)

Responsibilities:

* View assigned tasks
* Update task status
* Add task comments
* Cannot create or delete projects
* Cannot modify restricted fields

---

## Access Control

| User  | Read | Create | Update                 | Delete |
| ----- | ---- | ------ | ---------------------- | ------ |
| Alice | ✅    | ✅      | ✅                      | ✅      |
| Bob   | ✅    | ❌      | Status & Comments Only | ❌      |

---

## Workflow

1. Alice creates a project.
2. Alice assigns a task to Bob.
3. Bob updates task progress.
4. When Bob marks the task as completed:

   * Status is updated automatically.
   * Approval request is sent to Alice.
   * Alice receives a notification.
5. Alice reviews and approves the task.

